sentry_flutter.description: Sentry SDK for Flutter. This package aims to support different Flutter targets by relying on the many platforms supported by Sentry with native SDKs.

sentry.description: A crash reporting library for Dart that sends crash reports to Sentry.io. This library supports Dart VM and Web. For Flutter consider sentry_flutter instead.

sentry_dio.description: An integration which adds support for performance tracing for the Dio package.

sentry_logging.description: An integration which adds support for recording log from the logging package.

sentry_dart_plugin.description: A Dart Build Plugin that uploads symbols for Android, iOS/macOS, and Web to Sentry via sentry-cli.
